<template>
  <v-container>
  <v-row justify="center">
    <v-btn
        color="primary"
        dark
        @click.stop="dialog = true"
    >
      Open Dialog
    </v-btn>

    <v-dialog
        v-model="dialog"
        max-width="290"
    >
      <v-card>
        <v-card-title class="text-h5">
          Use Google's location service?
        </v-card-title>

        <v-card-text>
          Let Google help apps determine location. This means sending anonymous location data to Google, even when no
          apps are running.
        </v-card-text>

        <v-card-actions>
          <v-spacer></v-spacer>

          <v-btn
              color="green darken-1"
              text
              @click="dialog = false"
          >
            Disagree
          </v-btn>

          <v-btn
              color="green darken-1"
              text
              @click="dialog = false"
          >
            Agree
          </v-btn>
        </v-card-actions>
      </v-card>
    </v-dialog>
  </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  props: {
    isOpened: Boolean
  },
  data() {
    return {
      dialog: false,
    }
  },
}
</script>
